Name: Cortez Morris
Description:
Cortez was stabbed in the chest by Joseph Alexander.

> Cortez Morris, 18, of Valley Place near Margaret Street, Frankford, was fatally stabbed in the chest about 1 a.m. today on the sidewalk on 13th Street near Chestnut.
>
> Police said Joseph Alexander, 19, of Chester, was charged with murder and weapons offenses. Morris was stabbed, police said, during an argument between the two [people].

Source: United Press International, April 17, 1985
